Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.78,0:00:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中  川添珠姬选手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬选手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的家人到场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到停车场会面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联络过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之去看看吧  还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.32,0:00:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束前你就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧  比赛要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去给小西前辈加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那川添同学拜拜咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束我们就放你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要注意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为我们让小西前辈惹上了些奇怪的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣言这种东西真可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  大将
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你拯救部长  也就是纪梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是室江高的大将川添同学吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是东城高的小西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们下一场的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那三个人是我的后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是仰慕我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有时候却不分轻重跟要和我对战的对手开这种玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很高兴她们那么喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头我会好好教训她们的  这件事请…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更要紧的是不赶快的话比赛就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边比较快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分钟前了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段  你们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同学去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西前辈怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我们去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  要来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把球都扔在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛要开始了哦  川添同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君  荣花君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  事情处理完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  本来就没什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在整队了  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先锋  出列
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一击必杀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多…肚子…好疼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我忘记带便当过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家给了我好多好多好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没考虑接下来的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了就吃  给了就吃就吃就吃就吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强的气魄！没办法贸然出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！好难受！动不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都一动不动  她们在互相试探！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打呀！聪聪！先下手为强！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星也在注视着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚开始疼起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还要比赛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不还是出场了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是谁经过那里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是不是带了手机？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是检查过就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能把事情交给笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是关在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后闹大了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且本来不战而胜就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到她竟然摔得那么完美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,均衡被破坏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻上去！聪聪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东你怎么了？动作很差劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子真很不妙呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我总是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远足前一定会感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会之前一定会扭伤脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体怎么这么不争气！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步伐很乱  移动也畏畏缩缩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么利害的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻了啦  裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉！给我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经继续不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于舒畅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春天！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉的春天来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鼹鼠  你好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦  聪聪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚步变轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是假装的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么  有什么来临了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汹涌波涛向我涌来啊  各位！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪聪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了聪聪！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  炸肉饼…很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学  炸虾条…很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪莉我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步也动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是没什么大不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来解决你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地移动的话  就能突然发起进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对手的周围如同蜜蜂一般飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同蜜蜂一般刺下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！我的必杀技！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦  终于来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短暂的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧  胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔子  小鼹鼠  你们在哪里？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.05,0:11:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  东
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去医务室？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要在这里为大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个没有取胜的我至少做一些事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平手嘛  你不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场轮到小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放一百个心的看好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎同学…你要加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东！不要紧吧！怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！不错！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力已经相当娴熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上午的时候不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体好轻…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不要只想着取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做我能做到的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺地  赶快给我收拾掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子虽然是初学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆振倒是很锐利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊！小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不见了  幻觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点把这个忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我查过室江高的部团计划表
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也真是的  要比赛都不告诉人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复一下精神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中  集中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你都在干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都你很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不怎么好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子一平一负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点严峻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赢啊  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在这里打赢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来减轻你的负担！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:05.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上呀！小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你那脚  还能比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不比的话可就无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别弃权了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要被我堂堂正正的打败啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是剑道家的精神对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道这东西如果心境纷乱的话是无法变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说  如果要成为优秀的剑道家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面同样也要变得优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱有邪念之心的人是不会变强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剑道家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要打倒她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  差点到时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束  室江胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃  我做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起哦  小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就是一胜一败一平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是关键了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井口  不要后退！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙今天好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃！今天干劲十足呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与平日的集中力完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在母亲的事情上的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在全部用在了比赛上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是不怎么会注意他人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常注意力散漫的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她现在的紧张程度正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称Trance·Kirino
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的气势  是无法打倒纪梨乃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次径直取下两场！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天纪梨乃果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是纪梨乃真正的实力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃你干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天有神仙保佑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二胜一败一平  有希望！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一胜二败一平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说严峻  但小西如果能不被击中一次二连胜的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后按照取得点数的多少是我们赢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有取胜的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  你哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦！大将！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西同学  拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我败！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就推过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  凭你那脚还能架得住？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你那痛苦的表情呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚不还冷汗直冒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这眼神是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能退！这只是在强忍罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼得更紧一些…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她  认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是…发火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被压下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这样的家伙…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪里进攻都会被打中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不能攻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就来守！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要用反挑让她的进攻失效一次的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会漏出破绽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子…火焰剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢噢噢  好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺有效
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺击啊！是刺击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:26.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头一次在女子比赛里面看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是那么小的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么在这里突然就…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说她对这场比赛如此认真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…总觉得她的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是珠姬的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字还没出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别名吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧本里也一直都写着珠姬爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:24:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说我真的就叫作「珠姬爸爸」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说在生下珠姬之前就决定了「珠姬」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我从出生起就决定了要叫作「珠姬爸爸」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.86,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是何等深厚的父女羁绊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我家那珠姬大活跃的下一话是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大赛以及之后的室江高」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提我父母的名字叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「珠姬祖父」和「珠姬祖母」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.62,0:24:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是骗你的
